Set.Name: OnNew SQL
Set.Sql: INSERT INTO TRACE_SERVER (TS_NAME, TS_HOST, TS_PORT, TS_DATABASE, TS_UID, TS_PWD , TS_CDATE, TS_STATUS) VALUES (@TS_NAME, @TS_HOST, @TS_PORT, @TS_DATABASE, @TS_UID, @TS_PWD , @SYS_DATE, 'USED')

Set.Name: OnModify SQL
Set.Sql: UPDATE TRACE_SERVER SET TS_NAME = @TS_NAME, TS_HOST = @TS_HOST, TS_PORT = @TS_PORT, TS_DATABASE = @TS_DATABASE, TS_UID = @TS_UID, TS_PWD = case when @TS_PWD = '********' then TS_PWD ELSE ewa_func.encrypt(@TS_PWD) end, TS_MDATE = @SYS_DATE WHERE TS_ID = @TS_ID
